M|references|| Problem is frequent (weekly+) | 5 | 4 | 20 | 2 |
M|references|| Can acquire via cnt mkt | 4 | 4 | 16 | 3 |
M|references|| Team can build ML model | 4 | 3 | 12 | 4 |
M|references|| Users will share with colleagues | 3 | 4 | 12 | 5 |
M|references|| Market size is $1B+ | 3 | 2 | 6 | 6 |
M|references|**Impact (1-5):** How critical is this assumption to the business succeeding?
M|references|**Uncertainty (1-5):** How little evidence do you have?
M|references|**Priority Score:** Impact multiplied by Uncertainty. Higher score = test sooner.
