M|references|| Monthly subscription is preferred over annual | Medium | Pricing page A/B test |
M|references|| Self-serve onboarding is sufficient | High | Onboarding completion funnel |
M|references|| Integration with existing tools is required | Medium | Customer interviews about workflow |
M|references|| Freemium will drive paid conversions | High | Cohort analysis of free-to-paid |
M|references|| SMBs will pay without a sales call | Medium | Self-serve purchase funnel test |
